It's literally like
a slice of life.

00:24:20.004 --> 00:24:20.920
It could be your life.

00:24:20.920 --> 00:24:21.753
It could be my life.

00:24:21.753 --> 00:24:24.190
It could be your best
friend's life with you.

00:24:24.190 --> 00:24:27.370
So it's that kind of a film.

00:24:27.370 --> 00:24:29.560
And there is something.

00:24:29.560 --> 00:24:32.650
The message behind "Parched"
is absolutely wonderful,

00:24:32.650 --> 00:24:34.370
because the message
behind "Parched"

00:24:34.370 --> 00:24:37.870
is that women's empowerment
starts with women.

00:24:37.870 --> 00:24:41.550
It starts with every woman
standing up for herself.

00:24:41.550 --> 00:24:43.420
You may need a helping
hand sometimes,

00:24:43.420 --> 00:24:46.570
but it starts with
you, inside yourself.

00:24:46.570 --> 00:24:48.675
That power within you,
you have to access.

00:24:48.675 --> 00:24:49.800
And that's what "Parched"--

00:24:49.800 --> 00:24:50.841
PAVNI DIWANJI: Well said.

00:24:50.841 --> 00:24:51.406
Well said.

00:24:51.406 --> 00:24:53.720
