00:25:48.640 --> 00:25:52.460
have played multiple roles, are
taught to play multiple roles.

00:25:52.460 --> 00:25:54.430
That's why we're so
good at multitasking.

00:25:54.430 --> 00:25:57.750
So we're natural multi-taskers,
because we're sisters.

00:25:57.750 --> 00:26:00.060
We're daughters.

00:26:00.060 --> 00:26:02.170
We're children.

00:26:02.170 --> 00:26:06.020
We grew up, and we become
girlfriends, wives.

00:26:06.020 --> 00:26:09.080
AJAY DEVGN: What I meant
was, women, their roles

00:26:09.080 --> 00:26:09.730
keep changing.

00:26:09.730 --> 00:26:10.930
You know?

00:26:10.930 --> 00:26:16.310
They start from daughters,
sisters, girlfriends, wives,

00:26:16.310 --> 00:26:17.560
mothers.

00:26:17.560 --> 00:26:20.530
They keep evolving.

