A man is always a man.

00:26:27.190 --> 00:26:28.740
And we're born to be a man.

00:26:28.740 --> 00:26:30.500
Till he dies.

00:26:30.500 --> 00:26:32.490
And even when we
talk about "Parched,"

00:26:32.490 --> 00:26:34.450
it's just not about women.

00:26:34.450 --> 00:26:38.880
It's about the pressure
of society on men

00:26:38.880 --> 00:26:40.730
to do certain kind of things--

00:26:40.730 --> 00:26:41.490
KAJOL: And to remain
in a certain groove.

00:26:41.490 --> 00:26:43.230
AJAY DEVGN: --to show
that they are men.

00:26:43.230 --> 00:26:45.820
But you don't need to
prove that you're a man.

00:26:45.820 --> 00:26:46.960
You don't need to prove it.

00:26:46.960 --> 00:26:48.460
KAJOL: You don't
need to do whatever

00:26:48.460 --> 00:26:51.150
they say that you need to do
to prove that you're a man.

00:26:51.150 --> 00:26:53.360
AJAY DEVGN: So I think
women evolve faster,

00:26:53.360 --> 00:26:58.780
and that's why they grow
better, and men get stuck.

