00:27:09.400 --> 00:27:14.300
man was supposed to
[? ask ?] to-- I mean,

00:27:14.300 --> 00:27:18.110
Hindus, maybe, takes [INAUDIBLE]
or just leave the family

00:27:18.110 --> 00:27:20.770
and go away after
the age of 40, 45,

00:27:20.770 --> 00:27:23.900
because it is the same thing
that a man couldn't change.

00:27:23.900 --> 00:27:26.420
He always wanted
to rule the house.

00:27:26.420 --> 00:27:27.810
He wanted the power.

00:27:27.810 --> 00:27:30.460
And obviously, it's the
same lion mentality.

00:27:30.460 --> 00:27:32.430
You know, when the
other one has come,

00:27:32.430 --> 00:27:35.755
one has to leave the jungle.

00:27:35.755 --> 00:27:38.140
PAVNI DIWANJI: I think it's
really great to see you

00:27:38.140 --> 00:27:41.480
guys have such a great rapport
